<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hop" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hop,</orth> to jump, to skip: <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.168" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 168</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.304.168" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 304</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.304.168" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 304</bibl> <bibl n="shak. shr 4.3.98" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 3, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.2.179" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 2, 179</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.2.234" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 2, 234</bibl>. <emph>to h. without</emph> == to lose: <cit><quote>you shall h. without my custom,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 4.3.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 3, 99</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>would make thee quickly h. without thy head,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.140" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 3, 140</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>